        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your touch afflicts the target with goblin pox, an irritating allergenic rash. The target must attempt a Fortitude save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Goblin Pox</strong> (disease) <strong>Level</strong> 1. Goblins and goblin dogs are immune.</p>\n<p><strong>Stage</strong> <strong>1</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} (1 round)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} and the creature can't reduce its Sickened value below 1 (1 day)</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with goblin pox at stage 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is afflicted with goblin pox at stage 2.</p>"
